data.description: This farmhouse has so much charm and character! Just waiting for your TLC! Beautiful, antique features with the potential to be a stunning country home. With nearly an acre and half of land there is plenty of room for animals. As if that's not enough, there is a metal  detached garage that will hold 5 cars or anything else you desire!  Home is convenient to Yorktown Coast Guard Base, Langley Air Force Base and Fort Eustis Army Base. This property has been lived in and loved by its homeowners for the last 124 years and it's built to last. Three bedrooms, two baths, LR, DR, Kitchen, laundry and flex room. Home is sold as is, where is.
